sequenceDiagram
  participant JOB as Sufler_FullLoad
  participant BX as Bitrix_REST
  participant RAG as RAG_Index

  JOB->>BX: list elements page 1
  BX-->>JOB: IDs batch
  loop each article_id
    JOB->>BX: element.get
    BX-->>JOB: 200 body
    JOB->>RAG: Index
  end
  JOB->>BX: list next page
